---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="New Player Guide | Newcastle Table Tennis" description="First time at the club? Here's everything you need to know.">
  <div class="bg-neutral-50 py-24 min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-neutral-900 mb-6 font-heading uppercase">
          What to Expect
        </h1>
        <p class="text-2xl text-neutral-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto font-light">
          Everything you need to know before your first visit. We've answered the most common questions new players have.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
          <div class="relative h-80 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg group">
              <img src="/images/hall.jpg" alt="The Hall" class="w-full h-full object-cover transform group-hover:scale-105 transition duration-500" />
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 via-black/20 to-transparent flex flex-col justify-end p-8">
                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white font-heading uppercase mb-2">The Venue</h3>
                  <p class="text-white/90">Professional lighting, non-slip flooring, and ITTF approved tables at PCYC Broadmeadow.</p>
              </div>
          </div>
          <div class="relative h-80 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg group">
              <img src="/images/group-photo.jpg" alt="The People" class="w-full h-full object-cover transform group-hover:scale-105 transition duration-500" />
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 via-black/20 to-transparent flex flex-col justify-end p-8">
                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white font-heading uppercase mb-2">The Community</h3>
                  <p class="text-white/90">Friendly, welcoming, and passionate. Players of all ages and skill levels.</p>
              </div>
          </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-neutral-200 p-8 md:p-12">
        <div class="space-y-12">
            
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8">
                <div class="md:w-1/3">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 font-heading uppercase text-brand-600">Do I need equipment?</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="md:w-2/3">
                    <p class="text-lg text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
                        <strong class="text-neutral-900">No.</strong> We have plenty of average, beginners bats available for free use. If you have your own bats at home, feel free to bring them—many of our players bring their own equipment. Other members will be happy to guide you about your equipment and help you get the most out of it.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 border-t border-neutral-100 pt-12">
                <div class="md:w-1/3">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 font-heading uppercase text-brand-600">Am I good enough?</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="md:w-2/3">
                    <p class="text-lg text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
                        <strong class="text-neutral-900">Absolutely.</strong> We have a diverse community ranging from complete beginners to state-level competitors. Our session organizers will ensure you are matched with players of a similar skill level so everyone has a good game.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 border-t border-neutral-100 pt-12">
                <div class="md:w-1/3">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 font-heading uppercase text-brand-600">What does it cost?</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="md:w-2/3">
                    <ul class="space-y-4">
                        <li class="flex items-center text-lg text-neutral-700">
                            <span class="w-3 h-3 bg-brand-600 rounded-full mr-4"></span>
                            <span><strong>First Session:</strong> FREE</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center text-lg text-neutral-700">
                            <span class="w-3 h-3 bg-neutral-300 rounded-full mr-4"></span>
                            <span><strong>Concession:</strong> $8.50 per session</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center text-lg text-neutral-700">
                            <span class="w-3 h-3 bg-neutral-300 rounded-full mr-4"></span>
                            <span><strong>Junior (Under 18):</strong> $9.00 per session</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center text-lg text-neutral-700">
                            <span class="w-3 h-3 bg-neutral-300 rounded-full mr-4"></span>
                            <span><strong>Senior (18+):</strong> $9.50 per session</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center text-lg text-neutral-700">
                            <span class="w-3 h-3 bg-neutral-300 rounded-full mr-4"></span>
                            <span><strong>10 Session Pass:</strong> $88.50</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center text-lg text-neutral-700">
                            <span class="w-3 h-3 bg-neutral-300 rounded-full mr-4"></span>
                            <span><strong>Annual Membership:</strong> $40 (Adult) / $20 (Junior)</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 border-t border-neutral-100 pt-12">
                <div class="md:w-1/3">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 font-heading uppercase text-brand-600">What to wear?</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="md:w-2/3">
                    <p class="text-lg text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
                        Comfortable sports clothes. No light coloured shirts. Any equipment, if you have it.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 border-t border-neutral-100 pt-12">
                <div class="md:w-1/3">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 font-heading uppercase text-brand-600">Do I need to book?</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="md:w-2/3">
                    <p class="text-lg text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
                        <strong class="text-neutral-900">No booking required.</strong> Turn up any time after the session starts.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 border-t border-neutral-100 pt-12">
                <div class="md:w-1/3">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 font-heading uppercase text-brand-600">What if I'm not very good?</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="md:w-2/3">
                    <p class="text-lg text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
                        <strong class="text-neutral-900">That's perfectly fine!</strong> We welcome players of all skill levels. Many of our members started as complete beginners. Our session organizers will help match you with players at a similar level so you can enjoy a good game.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 border-t border-neutral-100 pt-12">
                <div class="md:w-1/3">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 font-heading uppercase text-brand-600">Is it competitive?</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="md:w-2/3">
                    <p class="text-lg text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
                        <strong class="text-neutral-900">It's up to you.</strong> We offer both competitive matches (on Monday and Wednesday) and purely social play (on weekends). You can choose what suits you. Many members enjoy both—competitive games when they want a challenge, and social games when they just want to relax and have fun.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-16 text-center">
         <a href="/timetable" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-10 py-4 border border-transparent text-lg font-bold rounded-md text-white bg-brand-600 hover:bg-brand-700 transition shadow-lg uppercase tracking-wide">
            View Timetable
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
